Man mein rahe vishwas bhi hardam
Jyoti kalash kabhi ho na maddhyam
Bole har gange..
Swar ki lehar mein ho harsh ki sargam
Goonje badan mein damroo ki dam-dam
Le ke chalein hum vijay ka parcham
Bole har gange..Shambho Shiv Shambho, Shiv-Shiv Shambho..
