Humne to seekha hai toofaan se takraana
Apna loha to duniya ne maana..
Hamse to mushkil hai dushman ka bach paana
Aag seene mein hai pala
Jal rahi saanson mein jwala
Hum to peete vish ka pyala
Saath apne trishul wala..Aa... aa... aa..
